,'',259.00,259.00,3,'2015-02-17 08:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'approved',NULL,'','','','Agriculture students and Plant Protectionists will be trained in IPM-TOT so they could expand the knowledge learnt to farmers to educate them in control of pests; training will cover the following topics.\r\n\r\n1.	General explaining of IPM\r\n2.	Introduction and kinds of pests\r\n1.	Effective agriculture practices to manage pest control\r\n2.	Strategic controls of pests\r\n3.	Chemical control of pests and\r\n4.	Biological control of pests\r\n\r\nThe following activities will be undertaken during implementation of the project:\r\n1.	Preparation of PA and BQ.\r\n2.	Selection of trainees.\r\n3.	Coordinate the training idea with the trainer and get their confirmation.\r\n4.	Preparation of training plan and training schedule.\r\n5.	Do necessary procurements. \r\n6.	Providing of training material.\r\n7.	Conducting the technical training according to the schedule\r\n8.	Pre and Post evaluation of the training.\r\n9.	Prepare training recommendation and completion report.  \r\n','','','2015-11-30 03:07:57','2015-11-30 03:07:57',NULL,NULL,NULL,8,NULL,NULL,8,67,3,3,11,'','','','',0,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,0.00,0.00,'',NULL),(275,NULL,'Develop Associations Structure','32550A025','','2.2.1 Association Capacity Building - Registration','','8500','32550L716','',0,'','Establishment of farmers’ association under the SAGAL program will make a linkage between farmers and fresh fruit traders/ input suppliers in local and national markets. In addition, will strength the value chain of Pomegranate & Grape fruits in the region. In addition, farmer’s product will be in different process stages and provide quality productions and categories in various grades to meet traders’ requirements.','2015-01-25 08:00:00','2015-02-05 08:00:00','','','','','',260.00,260.00,NULL,NULL,'2015-01-26 08:00:00',NULL,'2015-01-26 08:00:00',NULL,NULL,'approved',NULL,'',''