r and they will inform about SAGAL program. \r\n2.	MCA-SAGAL Agriculture Officer will identify the input supplier’ needs and requirements in the Nangarhar province. \r\n3.	MCA-SAGAL Agriculture Officer will analyzes their Needs \r\n4.	Procurement process\r\n5.	Delivered inputs (Okra seed, Cypermetrine) and promotional items to input supplier\r\n6.	Conducting field day and distribute packages to farmers for the expansion of input supplier business.\r\n7.	Provide completion report when input delivered to input supplier. \r\n','','','2015-12-14 10:01:18','2015-12-14 10:01:18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,10,4,67,3,NULL,11,'','','','',0,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','1$=AFN 55','2015-06-01',21725.00,27225.00,'',NULL),(599,NULL,'Training – CDCs – Sustain the Rule of Law - Nangarhar','32550A135','','5.3.1 District Development Planning','','8500','32550L745','',0,'','The CDCs members will understand about the Sustain the rule of law, and they will learn Law definition, sustain the rule of law senses, sustain the rule of law benefits, losses if we not have suitable sustain the rule of law, sustain the rule of law guidance (What is government responsibility on Sustain the rule of law? And what is the people responsibility on sustain the rule of law?), describing some Constitution articles which related on rule of law, sustain the rule of law effectiveness and efficiency and do on. As a result they know about sustain the rule of law importance in society and will learn about government responsibility to the local community and will learn how people can cooperate and coordinate with government.  \r\nThere will be a linkage between CDCs members and they will cooperate and coordinate between together in the next future.\r\n','2015-07-23 07:00:00','2015-11-30 08:00:00','','','','','',1569.00,1419.00,NULL,'2015-07-13 07:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,'','','','MC SAGAL Community Mobilization team will facilitate the Good Governance  trainin