 if implement the law in societies. \r\n2.	The CDCs Member will know better about the sustain the role of law and they never want Unsustainability of law in their village and district. \r\n','2015-07-23 07:00:00','2015-11-30 08:00:00','','','','','',1438.00,1258.00,NULL,'2015-07-12 07:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,'','','','1.	MCA-SAGAL community mobilization officer will prepare the list of participants who are going to participate in the Sustain the role of law training of the SAGAL program.\r\n2.	Send the invitation letters/phone calls to selected trainee to participate in Sustain the role of law training \r\n3.	Put PR and make a reasonable budget sheet for the expenditure of the Sustain the role of law training\r\n4.	Find suitable trainer for Sustain the role of law training. \r\n5.	Provide report on the training and make a conclusion of training.\r\n','','','2015-12-14 11:04:53','2015-12-14 11:04:53',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,10,4,67,3,NULL,11,'','','','',0,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','$1=AFN55','2015-07-12',69190.00,79090.00,'',NULL),(601,NULL,'Linkage Meetings – Farmers – Buyers - Kunar','32550A137','','1.2.3 Promote market and input services','','8500','32550L715','',0,'','To build linkages between farmers and buyers by sharing and jointly evaluating results, experiences and development.\r\nFarmers will link with fruits and vegetable buyers to provide their products on reasonable price and income generation for farmers and buyers. \r\n','2015-07-26 07:00:00','2016-12-30 08:00:00','','','','','',1538.00,1458.00,NULL,'2015-07-14 07:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,'','','','In this project there will be 4  linkage meetings arranging by SAGAL east for Tow targeted districts of Kunar province the totally 160 farmers, 12 buyers and 8 DAIL staff will be participate to discuss the problems and challenges they are facing and solution for those problems  \r\n\r\nThe following activities will be performing in this 